00:47:19,420 --> 00:47:21,540
So what is God doing in your heart?

683
00:47:21,540 --> 00:47:22,540
Let's pray.

684
00:47:22,540 --> 00:47:24,380
Father, we love You.

685
00:47:24,380 --> 00:47:26,380
We thank You for loving us.

686
00:47:26,380 --> 00:47:37,260
God, I pray this morning the Holy Spirit would take the Word of God and work.

687
00:47:37,260 --> 00:47:44,940
It's not for any individual to come and tell me necessarily what You're doing in their

688
00:47:44,940 --> 00:47:50,940
heart, but God, for us each individually to examine ourselves.

689
00:47:50,940 --> 00:47:52,900
Are You working?

690
00:47:52,900 --> 00:47:56,700
How are You working in our hearts?

691
00:47:56,700 --> 00:48:01,280
I pray that in this moment of invitation, if there's one that's lost, that's not sure

692
00:48:01,280 --> 00:48:06,580
of heaven, that today they would come forth, have a Bible that we could take and show them

693
00:48:06,580 --> 00:48:09,260
how they could know for sure that heaven is their home.

694
00:48:10,260 --> 00:48:16,260
And then God, I pray for Your people, those that are saved, God, maybe there's some here

695
00:48:16,260 --> 00:48:21,780
that say, to be honest, God's not really working in my heart.

696
00:48:21,780 --> 00:48:24,980
I've not spent time with Him in His Word as I should.

697
00:48:24,980 --> 00:48:25,980
I have a hard heart.

698
00:48:25,980 --> 00:48:29,300
I have a bitter heart.

699
00:48:29,300 --> 00:48:30,300
God's not working.

700
00:48:30,300 --> 00:48:35,380
We need to get that right with God this morning so that once again He could work in your heart

701
00:48:35,380 --> 00:48:36,380
and your life.

702
00:48:36,900 --> 00:48:39,740
Maybe this morning you know how God is working.

703
00:48:39,740 --> 00:48:42,020
You could articulate it clearly.

704
00:48:42,020 --> 00:48:45,220
Maybe this morning you need to come and just thank God that He's working in your heart.

705
00:48:45,220 --> 00:48:46,780
Don't take it for granted.

706
00:48:46,780 --> 00:48:47,780
Praise Him for it.

707
00:48:47,780 --> 00:48:50,260
Rejoice that He's working.

708
00:48:50,260 --> 00:48:52,820
God, I commit these moments to You.

709
00:48:52,820 --> 00:48:55,740
I pray that You'd move and work as only You can.

710
00:48:55,740 --> 00:48:58,100
We'll give You the glory for it's in Christ's name we pray.

711
00:48:58,100 --> 00:49:00,300
Would You stand with me?

712
00:49:00,300 --> 00:49:01,300
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

713
00:49:01,300 --> 00:49:05,180
Kimberly's going to play quietly on the piano and as she does, the altar is open.

